name: Desperate Reach (V)
Lore: 'If only someone had given Luke a hand.',
Text: 'Take Houjix or [Reflections II] R2-D2 into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR Cancel Dark Jedi Presence, I Have You Now, or Maul Strikes.
